### Create a new task with priority and recurring settings
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Weekly Team Meeting",
  "description": "Regular team sync-up",
  "priority": "high",
  "recurring_type": "weekly",
  "due_date": "2024-03-25T10:00:00.000Z"
}

### Create a task with dependencies
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Review Project",
  "description": "Review project deliverables",
  "priority": "medium",
  "due_date": "2024-03-26T15:00:00.000Z",
  "parent_task_id": 1
}

### Get all tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks

### Get high priority tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks?priority=high

### Get tasks with specific parent
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks?parent_task_id=1

### Update task status (mark as done)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "done"
} 